In this video, we'll explore the latest additions to the MSFS 2020 marketplace. This week, numerous training missions have been introduced at the airport. Additionally, two exciting new aircraft, the B2 Spirit and the C130-E, have been added, making it an excellent week for military aircraft enthusiasts.

Apart from these two categories, there are significant scenery enhancements, including new and updated airports, as well as improvements to various regions of the world.

A new feature this week is my top-3, where I'll share the items that are on my bucket list.
